CopyArrivalDate yes

IMAPStore gpm-far
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
User ***REMOVED***
PassCmd poauth2.py\ ~/gpm.token

MaildirStore gpm-near
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/

Channel gpm
Far :gpm-far:"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Near :gpm-near:gpm
Create Both
Expunge Both

##########

IMAPStore palm-far
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
User ***REMOVED***
PassCmd poauth2.py\ ~/palm.token

MaildirStore palm-near
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/

Channel palm-inbox
Far :palm-far:INBOX
Near :palm-near:palm
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel palm-drafts
Far :palm-far:Drafts
Near :palm-near:"palm/.drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel palm-sent
Far :palm-far:"Sent Items"
Near :palm-near:"palm/.sent"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel palm-spam
Far :palm-far:"Junk Email"
Near :palm-near:"palm/.spam"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Group palm
Channel palm-inbox
Channel palm-drafts
Channel palm-sent
Channel palm-spam

